Package curam.util.client.domain.defaults

Provides default values when no other values are available.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DomainDefault
    An interface for domain plug-ins that can provide the default value of a domain for use when no value is entered on a form by a user or when no value is available to initialize an input field displayed on a form.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDefault
    An abstract super-class for domain default value plug-ins.
    CodeTableCodeDefault
    Gets the default value for a code-table code.
    SvrBlobDefault
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_BLOB domain.
    SvrBooleanDefault
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_BOOLEAN domain.
    SvrCharDefault
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_CHAR domain.
    SvrDateDefault
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_DATE domain.
    SvrDateTimeDefault
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_DATETIME domain.
    SvrDateTimeDefaultCurrTime
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_DATETIME domain.
    SvrDoubleDefault
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_DOUBLE domain.
    SvrFloatDefault
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_FLOAT domain.
    SvrInt16Default
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_INT16 domain.
    SvrInt32Default
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_INT32 domain.
    SvrInt64Default
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_INT64 domain.
    SvrInt8Default
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_INT8 domain.
    SvrMoneyDefault
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_MONEY domain.
    SvrStringDefault
    The plug-in providing the default value for the SVR_STRING and SVR_UNBOUNDED_STRING domains.

Package curam.util.client.domain.defaults Description

Provides default values when no other values are available. The default values can be displayed in form fields to speed the entry of data by users.
